NEW YORK TRAP ROCK CORPORATION, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 208. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Feb. 2, 1931. Frederick W. Park, of New York City, for appellant. Howard W. Ameli, U. S. Atty., of Brooklyn, N. Y., and William E. Collins, Sp. Asst, to U. S. Atty., of New York City, for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
